{"tid":2107263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一同人鬧交之後就會開始怪自己/ 收埋自己","createTime":"2020-07-13T18:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T19:01:42.000Z","uid":2941,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1da6afdb536a3f84a34adcd8cd7e26418e7c500f","tid":2107263,"uid":2941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"次次一同人鬧交，或者係我單方面發晦氣<br />\n之後過咗陣就會覺得自己係咪應該收埋呢種情緒<br />\n會認為自己呢個行為會令人覺得自己唔夠好<br />\n其實可能都係無自信嘅一種表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係每次都咁<br />\n成日都好驚好自責<br />\n覺得自己唔應該有呢種情緒<br />\n會想收埋自己，覺得好唔開心<br />\n偽裝做咩都無所謂、無情緒嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁身邊嘅人就唔會討厭自己<br />\n情緒起伏好大咁，好唔鍾意咁嘅自己<br />\n覺得對方會頂自己唔順<br />\n一諗到咁就好想忍住呢啲負面情緒<br />\n全部吞晒落肚，自己喺房喊、唔開心都唔表現出嚟<br />\n咁就唔會做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底點先可以解決到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddd00834c6a3fb954438d75ac71c03ef22428ff","tid":2107263,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:13:39.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n男人老狗甘能廢-,-"},{"pid":"a2722fb0563d984e149cde8059771f42bc1e4b04","tid":2107263,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"一同人鬧交之後就會開始怪人地然後收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d508f8c41077c0164946f6796e9ca4016e86d7c8","tid":2107263,"uid":2941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a2722fb0563d984e149cde8059771f42bc1e4b04","tid":2107263,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"一同人鬧交之後就會開始怪人地然後收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:19:20.000Z","msg":"通常係怪完人哋之後反省，再怪返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75cecab065714ee0598a5ee93162e55a9273386","tid":2107263,"uid":95277,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc956a5e210baa07ce71a3c95fdf5d4c24fc13fc","tid":2107263,"uid":2941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75cecab065714ee0598a5ee93162e55a9273386","tid":2107263,"uid":95277,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得我呢啲人都係屈埋自己一個 唔好影響人就最好"},{"pid":"ec9e4cfca4df841d9a029219ebee9240b3c5666f","tid":2107263,"uid":14,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"會 明明唔開心果個係自己<br />\n甚至無做錯到啲咩<br />\n最後都會諗到自己唔啱<br />\n<br />\n自省係有需要嘅，但有時其實係over咗<br />\n仲會令自己好焦慮同情緒好差...."},{"pid":"09fa241679d0372892ada37efbbd8dee0b5726b3","tid":2107263,"uid":357463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T20:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f515f5a0733af092564d2a7cc810b90e856b0c","tid":2107263,"uid":225660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為自己開緊post, 由細到大都係咁, 明明好肯定自己嬲得合情合理, 都會無啦啦覺得好內疚好似搞到人地都唔開心埋, 或者懷疑自己overreacted<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申絲"},{"pid":"dd512277c1c78d79254ff51910a75418ac2fefa8","tid":2107263,"uid":84581,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14a001b8662c6f3a64ca52fcc4a023eaa17e289","tid":2107263,"uid":2941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58f515f5a0733af092564d2a7cc810b90e856b0c","tid":2107263,"uid":225660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1