>唔想害人，所以近排因為咁同男友提分手，佢話冷靜一排大家再諗下先，之後又開始覺得提分手係咪hurt到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁做搞到大家唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n不過又諗長痛不如短痛，唔想佢再受我d脾氣，好矛盾"},{"pid":"b8b74d76fbe85cf4eeb2ffe0b5d9def814d2e906","tid":2107263,"uid":2941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c52b0f9934012a9e0ff1ec9a624a33d77bf68ee","tid":2107263,"uid":180499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"以為自己出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想害人，所以近排因為咁同男友提分手，佢話冷靜一排大家再諗下先，之後又開始覺得提分手係咪hurt到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁做搞到大家唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n不過又諗長痛不如短痛，唔想佢再受我d脾氣，好矛盾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"可能佢無咁諗呢<br />\n依家當係比個機會自己靜下都好"},{"pid":"00397c98a39c2557eac1d3413060a133fc8a8455","tid":2107263,"uid":188960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f916c9093949785edcc271a9296089c1d58cc82e","tid":2107263,"uid":140113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"早排先發生呢個問題<br />\n明明成件事 全世界都有責任<br />\n但一嘈完交<br />\n我就會好自責 覺得係自己問題 自己錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf3df3bf1c7117c0115c084a57f4f34e1caf622","tid":2107263,"uid":149981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:13:29.000Z","msg":"一直都係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒咗人 人哋原諒咗我<br />\n最後自己怪自己<br />\n已經無辦法原諒到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}